 negotiation style."],[7599,7699,"She came prepared..."],[7699,7778,"Interesting."],[7778,8041,"Still waiting on that apology, Mr. Brooks."],[8041,8245,"If those get out, I'm done..."],[8299,8375,"Miss Stone..."],[8375,8604,"I apologize..."],[8604,8679,"Great!"],[8721,8837,"Now, what about the partnership?"],[8837,8954,"I'll sign."],[9813,9939,"Photo is deleted."],[9984,10122,"Be careful next time."],[10635,10823,"Well, well damn!"],[10852,11073,"Look at the girl boss go."],[11165,11236,"I'll assume you"],[11236,11394,"had nothing to do with this today."],[11536,11674,"But don't let it happen again."]],"6":[[66,183,"Are you threatening me?"],[233,325,"You know., the last person"],[325,391,"who threatened me."],[391,545,"now has grass over their grave."],[879,962,"Hey!"],[2058,2145,"Hey. Stop!"],[2145,2308,"What do you think? I'm an Uber driver?"],[2308,2425,"Would you cut the crap?"],[2450,2520,"Okay, drive,"],[2520,2712,"or I'm sleeping here tonight."],[2725,2795,"Fine!"],[3025,3145,"Then sleep here tonight."],[3395,3575,"If something happens to her in my car,"],[3575,3725,"that's gonna be a nightmare."],[3725,3862,"God damn it!"],[4012,4108,"Damn it!"],[5179,5258,"Get out."],[5883,5962,"Come on, get out."],[6187,6295,"She's burning up."],[6362,6450,"Not my problem."],[6500,6633,"Come on, Let's go, get out."],[6758,6891,"Okay, fine, sleep here then!"],[6891,6954,"Wait..."],[7758,7837,"Mom..."],[7891,7954,"Dad..."],[7954,8050,"What are you doing?"],[8058,8120,"Let go!"],[8120,8200,"Let go!"]],"7":[[1300,1391,"Just my luck, man!"],[1466,1545,"Come on."],[2541,2708,"I won't let you get away with it…"],[2970,3129,"You won't get away, Vincent…"],[3187,3266,"What?"],[3345,3454,"Vincent..."],[3454,3666,"You're into that bastard?!"],[4987,5229,"This is… The Hawke residence?"],[8808,8895,"Are you..."],[9116,9233,"Ryder's girlfriend?"],[9412,9483,"I'm not."],[9483,9633,"Oh, congrats."],[9662,9829,"You're the first girl he's ever brought home."],[9850,10041,"I know he seems i