u that?"],[7136,7273,"Yes, of course."],[7303,7403,"Sir."],[7403,7572,"Ryder will be here shortly."],[7574,7716,"Oh, good."],[7716,7891,"Tonight, I will make sure that"],[7891,8058,"Ryder agrees to this marriage."]],"18":[[29,237,"Tonight, I will make sure that"],[237,417,"Ryder agrees to this marriage."],[425,533,"To our families."],[588,690,"To family."],[690,754,"Yes, sir."],[1151,1226,"Ryder!"],[1338,1438,"You can't find..."],[1468,1597,"Whose engagement party?"],[1647,1868,"Um, ours, of course."],[1872,2060,"Does no one think my opinion matters?"],[2068,2160,"If your company wants the"],[2160,2293,"backing of the Benton family,"],[2335,2448,"you'll honor the agreement."],[2481,2706,"Then go to whoever made the agreement."],[2706,2873,"Oh, and by the way, congrats on"],[2873,3011,"your third marriage now."],[3011,3123,"Dad, enjoy it."],[3123,3326,"How dare you insult us?"],[3326,3474,"Oh, no, forgive him."],[3474,3716,"It's my fault. I didn't teach him manners."],[3774,3903,"Stop this right now."],[3949,4049,"Without their support,"],[4049,4175,"you will never beat your brother."],[4195,4284,"And you will never"],[4284,4421,"take over the company."],[4437,4537,"Take over the company?"],[4596,4804,"No one forces you to cheat"],[4804,5013,"and have that asshole Vincent."],[5150,5230,"What would your mom think"],[5230,5355,"if she saw you now?"],[5367,5584,"You have no right to speak about my mother."],[5709,5914,"Okay, Ryder, don't do this."],[5914,6031,"We can figure things out."],[6031,6097,"You know what?"],[6097,6289,"Give the company to whoever you want."],[6289,6398,"I don't care anymore."]],"19":[[963,1109,"Geez, throw yourself at me."],[1119,1263,"You bitch!"],[1263,1400,"How dare you flirt with Ryder"],[1400,1484,"in front of me!?"],[1739,1868,"Ow!"],[1910,2093,"Why are you defending her?"],[2093,2223,"Look how protective he is."],[2223,2373,"Something's definitely going on."],[2398,2592,"Yeah, their relationship seems"],[2592,2715,"really complicated."],[2727,2857,"It's a misunderstanding."],[2952,3090,"Vincent is my date."],[3240,3420,"Father arranges she be my date tonight."],[3420,3553,"I'd say it's a perfect match."],[3566,3770,"Then I guess we're all good then."],[3970,4029,"Here."],[4116,4195,"You'll like this."],[4233,4366,"She's allergic, actually."],[4387,4454,"Why do you know"],[4454,4575,"so much about her?"],[4658,4742,"Well, that's easy."],[4742,4888,"That's because we actually..."],[4888,5075,"No, he's not actually"],[5075,5213,"going to say it, is he?"]],"20":[[0,83,"Well, that's easy."],[83,237,"That's because we actually..."],[237,383,"Stay calm, Eliza."],[383,554,"You can't let Daisy and Mr. Hawke know"],[554,696,"what happened that night!"],[696,892,"Miss Benton, I'm his boss."],[892,1051,"I've taken him to a few dinners."],[1051,1217,"Yes, that's right."],[1222,1326,"So, you're the one"],[1326,1480,"who's always preventing"],[1484,1630,"Ryder from seeing me."],[1639,1764,"Our work is demanding."],[1764,1922,"Yes, but I've never stopped him"],[1922,2014,"from seeing you."],[2022,2193,"Ladies and gentlemen."],[2198,2314,"Now that we've resolved"],[2314,2448,"all these misunderstandings,"],[2448,2523,"why don't we get back to"],[2523,2631,"the engagement party?"],[2631,2731,"What do you say?"],[2740,2932,"Please have some cake and other delights."],[2944,3028,"Thank you!"],[3128,3265,"I'm going to use the restroom."],[3265,3361,"Of course."],[3841,3991,"I'll show you who's boss."],[4512,4592,"You!"],[4704,4804,"Ryder!"],[4821,5038,"Have you seen Rider or Eliza?"],[5071,5338,"Both missing at the same time?"],[5543,5607,"Go tell Miss Benton"],[5607,5772,"Ryder is in the upstairs guest room."]],"21":[[19,95,"Go tell Miss Benton"],[95,250,"Ryder is in the upstairs guest room."],[984,1084,"Mr. Hawke!"],[1084,1184,"Let's go find them."],[1263,1363,"Right now!"],[1739,1910,"So, you really like that bastard Vincent?"],[2381,2569,"If Daisy and Adrian see this,"],[2569,2671,"I'll have to leave Everon"],[2671,2802,"and my revenge will end here…"],[3073,3169,"What? Are you scared?"],[3219,3315,"What do you want from me?"],[3453,3549,"Rye?"],[3549,3641,"Are you in there?"]],"22":[[208,350,"Ryder, open this door!"],[350,462,"I know you're inside!"],[475,578,"Open the door right now"],[578,679,"and come out!"],[679,784,"Someone said they saw him"],[784,909,"inside with that woman."],[917,996,"You don't think they're..."],[996,1192,"What is with all the noise?"],[1197,1276,"Rye!"],[1292,1455,"I thought you were inside."],[1455,1580,"So, what's with all the yelling?"],[1885,2018,"Miss Ben?"],[2018,2143,"Mr. Hawke?"],[2143,2318,"I was just taking a nap."],[2489,2556,"Remember,"],[2556,2723,"you still owe me again, Eliza."],[3374,3480,"Well, this was all"],[3480,3641,"just a misunderstanding."],[3641,3812,"Eliza's a woman of integrity."],[3828,4049,"She wouldn't be involved with Ryder."],[4074,4237,"My apologies, Eliza."],[4270,4400,"No worries."],[4400,4533,"Congratulations."],[4533,4821,"Wishing you a lifetime of happiness."],[5009,5125,"You really mean that?"]],"23":[[41,154,"Sucker."],[154,287,"Well, uh, yes."],[287,571,"Thank you so much, Miss Stone."],[638,779,"I knew I was right about you."],[788,963,"The company is doing better"],[963,1121,"and Ryder's not hanging around"],[1121,1222,"with lowlifes anymore,"],[1267,1601,"Let's just say he's young and impulsive."],[1626,1705,"But,"],[1764,1822,"smart."],[1822,1864,"I'm sorry."],[1864,1989,"Who are you calling impulsive?"],[1989,2047,"See, Rye."],[2047,2198,"She doesn't appreciate you."],[2198,2394,"I don't remember asking you what kind of deal."],[2414,2590,"Well, I'm your fiancée!"],[2673,2898,"Mr. Hawke, look at him."],[2898,3174,"Ryder, with me now. Come on!"],[3282,3374,"What's that?"],[3482,3591,"It was my dog."],[3620,3766,"Ryder is mine."],[3803,3912,"Stay away from him!"],[3912,4003,"Miss Benton."],[4020,4187,"Why don't you just take care of your own man"],[4187,4454,"instead of acting like an insecure phycho?"],[4679,4850,"Just you wait, bitch!"]],"24":[[467,575,"I received word,"],[696,850,"Vincent has a flash drive."],[890,980,"What's on it"],[980,1117,"is enough to bring him down."],[1117,1213,"It's our only shot."],[1292,1388,"I'll find it."],[1601,1722,"This is a good chance."],[1918,2001,"Excuse me,"],[2060,2202,"which room is Vincent's?"],[2227,2331,"Oh, that door."],[2448,2527,"Thank you."],[2969,3023,"Vincent?"],[3194,3278,"Are you in there?"],[5551,5697,"This one's been met a lot."],[6310,6431,"He was engaged?"],[6456,6577,"She looks familiar..."],[7778,7887,"Vincent's birthday!"],[8566,8666,"The date on the photo!"]],"25":[[617,785,"Too risky to keep going."],[785,925,"The alarm could go off."],[1847,1926,"This should do it."],[1960,2139,"Won't take long before I have the code."],[3799,3958,"Did you just come out from his bedroom?"],[4041,4175,"This is about my parents,"],[4204,4383,"I can't let him find out."],[4387,4487,"Personal."],[4507,4612,"It doesn't concern you."],[4625,4754,"This is my house."],[4754,4875,"I'm pretty sure it does concern me."],[4879,4996,"I can't let this get out."],[5013,5159,"I do like Vincent."],[5159,5342,"I'm just trying to get to know him better."],[5397,5605,"You'll... keep my secret, won't you?"],[5605,5734,"Great taste of men."],[5734,5805,"Well done."],[5805,6035,"Did Vincent used to be engaged?"],[6035,6193,"He told you about his ex-wife?"],[6193,6278,"Wow, okay."],[6278,6535,"So, he's out here spilling family secrets to you."],[6544,6681,"Ex-wife?"]],"26":[[8,112,"Ex-wife?"],[112,333,"So, he used to be married, not just engaged?"],[342,479,"What? You getting jealous now?"],[529,771,"If I like someone, nothing like that matters."],[771,846,"I'm warning you,"],[846,1076,"Vincent is not what he seems."],[1076,1267,"Loving someone takes courage."],[1313,1459,"I'm not scared."],[1459,1589,"Then don't come crying to me"],[1589,1744,"when you end up in a psych ward."],[1926,2093,"You mean Vince? He..."],[2615,2694,"Oh!"],[2706,2795,"Haha..."],[2877,3069,"Ryder Hawke! What is wrong with you?"],[3069,3253,"I'm just giving back what you owe me."],[3286,3370,"Next time,"],[3370,3478,"Don't let me hear his name"],[3478,3553,"Come out of your mouth."],[3553,3654,"Do you understand me?"],[4179,4258,"Haha."],[6085,6260,"Did you see anyone enter my room?"]],"27":[[70,258,"Did you see anyone enter my room?"],[1197,1309,"Don't be afraid."],[1388,1472,"Just tell me."],[1472,1522,"No."],[1572,1668,"No one."],[1818,1935,"Are you sure?"],[1985,2064,"Yes."],[2127,2344,"Sir, we have the footage."],[2444,2540,"Let's see."],[3211,3290,"If no one was here,"],[3290,3378,"then get back to work."],[3378,3440,"Yes, sir."],[3499,3578,"Sir."],[3793,3850,"That book was moved."],[3850,3983,"But the footage is clean."],[3983,4095,"Who the hell was it?"],[4483,4658,"Sir, you saved my life."],[4658,4775,"I won't take money."],[4821,4900,"No."],[5605,5880,"The surveillance was taken care of with AI."],[5890,5984,"Good."],[6047,6277,"And while you're at it, look into Eliza for me."]],"28":[[2035,2118,"Go ahead."],[2139,2243,"I'll wait right here."],[2620,2810,"I'll find out exactly what you were doing"],[2810,2909,"in Vincent's room."],[2977,3090,"Weird."],[3090,3299,"Ryder used to hate her,"],[3315,3503,"now he follows her everywhere."],[3541,3762,"I heard he bailed on his engagement to Daisy."],[3799,3887,"Maybe it's because of her..."],[3887,3962,"Excuse me."],[4033,4095,"What was that?"],[4095,4204,"Miss Benton."],[4229,4362,"Nothing, madam."],[4362,4600,"It was a dress issue that night"],[4600,4792,"because of that old woman."],[4800,4879,"Got it?"],[5004,5084,"Hmm."],[5284,5405,"What are you doing here?"],[5417,5623,"It's been forever since we went on a date."],[5623,5726,"I'm working."],[6835,7023,"Oh, those three."],[7057,7178,"It's like a soap opera."],[7184,7244,"Yeah."],[8387,8477,"I'll take you home."],[8546,8629,"No need."],[8775,8942,"Ryder, you're free!"],[9263,9365,"Let's go on our date."],[9365,9496,"I'm not free."],[9496,9684,"Stop acting like I owed you something"],[9684,9818,"just because I like you."],[9830,10072,"I am the Benton family heiress."],[10072,10235,"Oh, then please be my guest."],[10235,10343,"Find someone else."],[10543,10643,"Just you wait!"],[11311,11402,"Let go."],[11402,11537,"I have a date tonight."],[11537,11703,"Oh, with who? That bastard?"],[11703,11807,"None of your business."],[11815,12107,"She clearly didn't listen to a word I said."],[12120,12236,"If you don't tell me who,"],[12299,12508,"then I'll tell Vincent about everything."],[12883,12991,"No, you won't."]],"29":[[421,567,"Vincent is out in a meeting."],[567,725,"I have to move fast."],[2640,2940,"Wait, this is Ryder's birthday."],[2970,3078,"Why?"],[3983,4062,"What?"],[4176,4317,"Intruder in Mr. Hawke's room."],[4518,4615,"Check every corner."],[5259,5325,"Damn it!"],[5412,5510,"It's a trap."],[6110,6247,"There! Grab her!"],[6952,7057,"The bathroom in his room."],[7119,7240,"I can escape through the window."],[7599,7663,"Oh!"],[8262,8341,"Eliza?"]],"30":[[4,171,"How are you doing in my house?"],[421,500,"Open up!"],[675,846,"Please! Help me!"],[846,1009,"Why don't you get that bastard to help you?"],[1009,1159,"Please, I really need you."],[1159,1251,"Alright."],[1355,1539,"But you have to beg until I'm satisfied."],[3299,3386,"Let's break it down."],[3636,3799,"Sir, we're looking for an intruder."],[3995,4099,"Are you looking to piss me off?"],[4099,4183,"Or are you trying to die?"],[4212,4312,"Relax, brother."],[4312,4429,"We're just chasing the thief."],[4429,4637,"Someone took something important from my room."],[4654,4745,"He's here too?"],[4745,4896,"If they find me, I'm done!"],[4896,5000,"A thief?"],[5037,5275,"Or it's just an excuse to come out."],[5275,5350,"Get out!"],[5350,5522,"If there's nothing, we'll leave."]],"31":[[100,250,"If there's nothing, we'll leave."],[250,462,"I said get out!"],[525,673,"So defensive."],[673,804,"Oh, don't tell me..."],[867,1005,"You know the theif, don't you?"],[1005,1222,"Look, if you ruin my bath again,"],[1251,1401,"I'll have to use force."],[1426,1568,"Better not push this lunatic."],[1772,1893,"Just search the bedroom."],[1914,2043,"Yes, sir."],[2631,2748,"It's already been a minute."],[2811,2927,"Hope she's okay in there."],[2932,3078,"What are you checking your phone for?"],[3144,3211,"You busy?"],[3211,3520,"No, I'm just trying not to look at your ugly ass face."],[3574,3770,"You want your thief, you better hurry up."],[4583,4672,"Come on, Ryder."],[4672,4778,"Don't let a petty thief"],[4778,4984,"ruin this rare brotherly moment."],[4988,5188,"Oh, cut the act."],[5651,5822,"Hang in there, Eliza."],[5839,5997,"I'm sorry. Mom, Dad."],[5997,6131,"I wasn't strong enough."]],"32":[[667,713,"Hey, hey, hey!"],[713,908,"Don't touch my shit!"],[2100,2156,"Boss."],[2156,2242,"Surveillance shows"],[2242,2402,"the intruder escaped through the back."],[2414,2531,"Understood."],[2670,2736,"Oh."],[2840,3015,"Look, dear, our little one-on-one is over."],[3366,3473,"Now I have to shower."],[3473,3582,"I feel dirty."],[3624,3703,"We're done!"],[3803,3883,"Let's go."],[4290,4374,"Eliza..."],[4443,4568,"Eliza! Stay with me!"],[4680,4783,"Eliza!"],[4863,4984,"Eliza, come on. Come on."],[5000,5163,"It's okay. Come on. Stay with me!"],[5764,6010,"Why am I still seeing Ryder Hawke"],[6010,6120,"in the afterlife?"],[6177,6394,"Unfortunately, you're not dead."],[6702,6798,"Eliza! Stay with me!"],[7119,7290,"Thank you. But I'm leaving."],[7369,7570,"What? Off to see that bastard again?"],[7653,7774,"None of your business."]],"33":[[408,571,"This is your reward for helping?"],[1142,1288,"Then let me return the favor."],[2327,2439,"Hey, hey, hey!"],[2502,2719,"Hey, I'm just trying to help you."],[2811,2969,"So why did you keep pushing me away?"],[2998,3136,"Because this is my fight."],[3215,3424,"I don't want anyone else to be dragged into it."],[3511,3581,"Come here."],[4124,4204,"Thank you."],[4244,4320,"Watch your step."],[4909,5030,"Can I be catching a cold?"],[5257,5370,"Let's get out of here."],[5568,5668,"I knew it!"],[5693,5889,"You two won't get away with this."]],"34":[[421,604,"Don't worry, gonna be great."],[1284,1430,"Okay, now that everyone's here,"],[1430,1739,"we can begin the vote to confirm Eliza Stone as"],[1739,1956,"Everon's new CEO."],[1964,2181,"No doubt Miss Stone is a talent."],[2256,2389,"Since she took over,"],[2389,2585,"Everon's R&D has skyrocketed."],[2615,2719,"Not only has our"],[2752,2911,"stock value skyrocketed,"],[2911,3065,"but what I'm most pleased about"],[3065,3353,"is that Ryder is now acting like a true successor."],[3420,3718,"Well, Miss Stone does keep me in check."],[4625,4704,"Miss Stone?"],[4822,4916,"Uh."],[4975,5117,"Um, this is..."],[5138,5513,"all thanks to Mr. Hawke for giving me a chance."],[5513,5726,"Oh, come on, of course."],[5759,5926,"Now, if Ryder can just finalize"],[5926,6056,"the marriage with Daisy,"],[6056,6197,"everything would be perfect."],[6256,6464,"Dad, today's Eliza's day."],[6464,6664,"Yes, yes, indeed it is."],[6781,7136,"Then, I declare Eliza Stone..."],[7136,7261,"Wait!"]],"35":[[0,79,"Wait!"],[254,371,"Mr. Hawke,"],[371,533,"I have something to show you that"],[592,846,"might make you reconsider handing her"],[880,1026,"the title of CEO."],[1230,1317,"What is on that?"],[1317,1530,"Whether I show you or not"],[1609,1768,"depends on Ryder's attitude."],[1847,1926,"What are you doing?"],[1926,2143,"Trying to ruin someone else's big day?"],[2298,2377,"Sweetie."],[2519,2681,"Don't think I don't know"],[2681,2890,"what happened between you and that tramp"],[2890,3006,"back at the mansion."],[3253,3386,"Okay, what do you want?"],[3386,3478,"Marry me."],[3999,4045,"No."],[4066,4129,"No?"],[4162,4241,"No!"],[4320,4612,"Then don't blame me for what happens next."],[4925,5066,"If Eliza's fired,"],[5066,5239,"Vincent suspects anything,"],[5239,5347,"he'll destroy her."],[5422,5492,"Okay,"],[5518,5655,"Fine. I.."],[5851,5930,"Miss Benton,"],[6018,6118,"show whatever you want."],[6135,6235,"Don't regret."]],"36":[[8,212,"Miss Stone, please explain."],[271,392,"Explain?"],[437,774,"She violated her contract and seduced Ryder!"],[780,834,"Bullshit!"],[834,1034,"That's... that's bullshit. Dad."],[1034,1251,"She's saying whatever she wants to marry me."],[1251,1397,"Oh, enough. Ryder."],[1409,1522,"Daisy's your fiancée."],[1689,1939,"Mr. Hawke, I'm Ryder's superior."],[1939,2077,"It's been completely professional."],[2077,2181,"Bullshit!"],[2181,2431,"That night at dinner, I spilled wine on my top."],[2439,2615,"It was cold, so I borrowed a shirt."],[2615,2669,"That's all."],[2669,2765,"Liar!"],[2765,2877,"Enough!"],[3044,3128,"I believe you."],[3132,3228,"Mr. Hawke!"],[3257,3552,"But I will be transferring you out of Everon"],[3552,3716,"and you can head up one of our other companies."],[3737,3837,"Mr. Hawke, I..."],[3862,4083,"know you're doing this to separate me and Ryder."],[4083,4283,"But that's completely unnecessary."],[4458,4775,"I, Eliza Stone, resign as current CEO of Everon AI."],[4796,4846,"What?"],[4846,4963,"I'll no longer see Ryder again."]],"37":[[33,354,"I, Eliza Stone, resign as current CEO of Everon AI."],[379,408,"What?"],[408,550,"I'll no longer see Ryder again."],[550,725,"But Miss Stone, this is not ..."],[725,771,"Mr. Hawke,"],[771,884,"my decision's been made."],[925,988,"But don't worry."],[988,1113,"Ryder has everything he needs to be"],[1113,1242,"a true successor."],[1359,1438,"Eliza."],[1505,1597,"You don't need her family's"],[1597,1705,"resources anymore."],[2069,2131,"Bitch!"],[2131,2286,"What the hell does that mean?"],[2298,2377,"Okay, Daisy."],[2377,2506,"We apologize"],[2506,2681,"that this engagement didn't work out."],[2681,2827,"But as compensation,"],[2873,3006,"we will give the Benton family"],[3006,3153,"a couple more shares of our company."],[3153,3453,"Ugh, we don't need your damn charity."],[3541,3707,"Jesus Christ!"],[4662,4884,"After investigation, the couple was"],[4884,5052,"killed in a gang shootout."],[5092,5246,"The shooter is now in custody…"],[5276,5480,"This is Zoe Hart from NEWS.com"],[5480,5563,"Zoe Hart…"],[5626,5772,"So you're the one protecting him."],[6652,6760,"Wiped clean."],[6802,6956,"Now convenient."],[6956,7094,"According to my research,"],[7094,7340,"he was always going to the nearby suburban town."],[7344,7490,"And Ryder once said..."],[7574,7706,"Then don't come crying to me"],[7706,7854,"when you end up in a psych ward."],[8500,8579,"Got you."],[9409,9601,"So you indeed hid the thief that night."]],"38":[[1146,1226,"So,"],[1366,1513,"who entered my room that day?"],[1609,1692,"No..."],[1793,1943,"Please! Please!"],[1981,2061,"Be honest,"],[2155,2285,"and I won't hurt you."],[2694,2824,"It was a woman!"],[3012,3155,"It was a woman..."],[4479,4583,"She brought it on herself."],[4583,4669,"Of course, sir."],[5121,5313,"I would like to officially announce"],[5347,5463,"that Everon AI"],[5463,5618,"will now be under Ryder's management."],[5709,5814,"Ryder?"],[5814,5964,"Isn't he still too green?"],[6064,6243,"Well, to his concerns,"],[6243,6460,"Vincent will act as his supervisor."],[6510,6564,"Well,"],[6564,6749,"with Vincent helping, I feel reassured."],[6869,6943,"Well, to make sure that"],[6943,7168,"this acquisition goes through smoothly,"],[7168,7441,"Ryder will not have any further communication"],[7441,7580,"with the former CEO."],[7595,7801,"That's strictly for security reasons."],[8003,8153,"So, you still don't trust me."],[8904,9103,"Please ignore his overreaction,"],[9117,9242,"He does it all the time."]],"39":[[442,521,"Fuck, what is wrong with you?"],[521,608,"Are you following me?"],[608,726,"Father's orders."],[800,896,"I have no say."],[900,1051,"You wanna watch me take a dump, too?"],[1059,1159,"So disgusting."],[1159,1280,"No, I'll wait outside."],[1584,1726,"Since you're hiding that thief,"],[1747,1897,"I'll just let you lead me to her."],[2248,2515,"No one has ever visited the patient in Room 103."],[2594,2694,"Are you a relative?"],[2831,2972,"He's my ex."],[2980,3153,"I only recently found out he was here."],[3332,3490,"Miss Carter, we're here."],[3527,3632,"Thank you."],[3812,4020,"I didn't think that old man could get"],[4020,4191,"Such a young lover."],[4650,4746,"Who are you?"],[5004,5088,"Good night."]],"40":[[312,392,"Who are you?"],[446,567,"Do you remember this man?"],[867,975,"I don't know him."],[1092,1372,"Six years ago, you reported this story of my parents."],[1372,1555,"The couple was killed in a gang shootout."],[1584,1701,"Do you know the truth?"],[1785,1902,"Baby."],[1947,2198,"Yes, baby. Mommy got you water."],[2260,2398,"Look, stop. He..."],[2431,2473,"Ah!"],[2473,2731,"He locked you here to cover himself."],[2731,2952,"Aren't you mad? Don't you even care?"],[3474,3591,"Of course I care."],[3624,3870,"But what am I meant to do? Everyone thinks I'm crazy."],[3928,4045,"I can help you."],[4642,4772,"Is that the USB that holds the"],[4772,4890,"evidence of Vincent's crime?"],[5105,5184,"Zoe!"],[5309,5442,"She locked the door again!"],[5467,5601,"Doctors are coming. We don't have much time!"],[5601,5809,"Please, just trust me!"]],"41":[[320,404,"Which one?"],[845,920,"Oh my god."],[920,1116,"Hi, yes, baby, I love you."],[1179,1354,"I love. Do you love me?"],[1362,1562,"That woman who"],[1562,1675,"visited the old man today seemed odd."],[1758,1933,"What? Someone might have been in Zoe's room?"],[1966,2133,"Alright, wait there for me."],[2212,2354,"Hey, big bro."],[2354,2425,"Where you headed?"],[2558,2595,"Nowhere."],[2646,2738,"Aren't you my guardian?"],[2738,2879,"You completely disappeared on me."],[2900,2920,"And?"],[2954,3069,"Thought I heard Zoe's voice."],[3069,3205,"Is she back or..."],[3205,3391,"I thought you said"],[3450,3562,"she had some men and"],[3562,3675,"fled the country or..."],[3675,3791,"She's recently"],[3816,3933,"returned."],[3933,4054,"I'm just going to check on her."],[4054,4175,"Oh."],[4212,4291,"Got it."],[4291,4341,"No need to worry,"],[4341,4424,"I'll just do that myself."],[4445,4491,"Well,"],[4491,4595,"the old man said"],[4641,4700,"I couldn't leave your sight."],[4700,4904,"So, how about we go together?"]],"42":[[154,350,"What a lucky old man."],[955,1047,"I won't let you down."],[1238,1287,"You know what?"],[1317,1430,"You've actually been really well-behaved."],[1443,1509,"No need for"],[1543,1669,"24/7 monitoring."],[1689,1755,"I'll talk to Dad."],[1885,1945,"Thanks, bro."],[2610,2717,"We're going to see Zoe tonight."],[2761,2894,"Have someone keep an eye on Ryder."],[3265,3318,"Zoe?"],[3503,3566,"You WEre my wife."],[3670,3741,"I know you too well."],[4254,4387,"Did someone come visit you today?"],[4487,4654,"Don't lie to me."]],"43":[[12,179,"Don't lie to me."],[221,375,"You ruined my life!"],[475,550,"Her child..."],[550,671,"Oh, you forget I was a father."],[725,829,"I was heartbroken too."],[871,921,"It was the only way"],[921,1063,"I could justify locking you away."],[1121,1183,"Vincent,"],[1222,1463,"I regret ever being your wife"],[1463,1601,"and covering for you!"],[1760,1859,"This is your fault."],[1939,2068,"If you weren't such a fucking insane,"],[2068,2176,"maybe we could've been happy."],[2544,2580,"David."],[3032,3149,"Ma'am, please."],[3303,3398,"Take your medicine."],[3445,3599,"I can't stand to see you suffer like this."],[3666,3824,"No, I won't take it!"],[4003,4186,"I want to stay alive and watch you die!"],[4204,4275,"Ma'am, please!"],[4275,4341,"No!"],[4404,4533,"Please calm down, you!"],[4608,4629,"No!"],[4733,4750,"No!"],[4796,4817,"No!"],[4850,4879,"No!"],[4929,4963,"No!"],[5067,5088,"No!"],[5150,5171,"No!"],[5213,5242,"No!"],[5284,5305,"No!"],[5372,5419,"No!"],[5426,5500,"No!"],[5968,6076,"I always love you, Zoe."],[6148,6280,"You're a monster!"],[6280,6425,"You're gonna go to hell!"]],"44":[[200,404,"Sounds your daughter's birthday is coming up."],[754,905,"Thank you for your thoughtfulness."],[1488,1547,"Just"],[1547,1751,"gonna pretend I don't exist or what?"],[1760,1893,"I don't work at Everon anymore,"],[1893,1964,"Mr. Hawke."],[1997,2163,"We were practically strangers."],[2289,2469,"He's an old colleague."],[2469,2535,"Let's go."],[2535,2635,"Let me get this straight."],[2686,2802,"You left me for..."],[2877,2982,"That?"],[3432,3607,"Well, let's not forget about your new woman,"],[3607,3661,"shall we?"],[4029,4128,"Go shopping with your friends."],[4625,4709,"Excuse me, sir."],[4709,4804,"I'm gonna be renting out"],[4804,4925,"this entire establishment"],[4925,4975,"for the night."],[5246,5301,"Let go."],[5359,5488,"You must forgot who I am."],[5588,5697,"So let me remind you."]],"45":[[1184,1301,"After all this time,"],[1301,1459,"you still like it rough, huh?"],[1480,1530,"Rough?"],[1630,1730,"I'm sorry, but weren't you"],[1730,1875,"the one saying yes"],[1875,2060,"over and over again that night?"],[2173,2293,"Oh, and what about that old man?"],[2293,2378,"You still like him?"],[2381,2427,"Well,"],[2469,2580,"what's the woman to do"],[2580,2870,"when man in power like yourself bully us?"],[2927,3014,"Bully you?"],[3123,3257,"Babe, I'm just having fun."],[3390,3478,"Well,"],[3506,3690,"I'm in a rush, so is..."],[3690,3857,"five minutes okay?"],[3883,3999,"Hear you're improving."],[4012,4108,"I am."],[4108,4295,"Let's see if you can handle it."],[5096,5217,"Are you always this dull?"],[5342,5508,"You know we're just having fun, right?"],[5551,5658,"Mr. CEO,"],[5658,5780,"you're gonna have fun now, huh?"],[5809,5914,"You know, thanks to you,"],[5914,6035,"I finally have a day off, so..."],[6068,6093,"Oh."],[6239,6360,"I've managed to shake off"],[6360,6498,"Vincent's spies for now."],[6498,6610,"So, tell me about your plan."],[6673,6769,"Maybe I can help."],[6773,6840,"How do you know?"]],"46":[[75,166,"So,"],[166,397,"I don't have Vincent's connections,"],[442,595,"But I do have ties to the underground."],[617,721,"You came to our family"],[721,900,"because you suspected Vincent killed"],[900,1076,"your parents six years ago,"],[1096,1134,"right?"],[1151,1184,"You know?"],[1238,1343,"Of course."],[1343,1518,"This involves my family too."],[1535,1664,"Mr. Walker already helped"],[1664,1801,"alter my family records,"],[1801,1931,"but he still found out."],[1951,2052,"Then Vincent must've...."],[2135,2260,"You know, you should be thanking me."],[2260,2360,"Without me,"],[2360,2488,"Vincent would have all your information."],[2523,2548,"You..."],[2610,2802,"Remember when you went to Vincent's room?"],[2819,2977,"Guess who wiped all the security footage"],[2977,3186,"and told you where the cameras were?"],[3457,3653,"You went to see Zoe, right?"],[3899,3937,"Eliza,"],[3949,4091,"You know all of his people are"],[4091,4179,"in that hospital."],[4229,4366,"He's bound to find out."],[4366,4487,"I'm not afraid."],[4617,4721,"You're not afraid."],[4813,4977,"You're not CEO anymore,"],[4977,5055,"Eliza."],[5096,5168,"If I'm not around"],[5168,5296,"and he wants to kill you,"],[5296,5380,"he can."],[5380,5451,"I know."],[5459,5559,"But"],[5559,5672,"it's my decision."]],"47":[[12,183,"They're my parents."],[183,278,"You would do the same thing"],[278,358,"if it were you."],[558,641,"Mom."],[2300,2406,"Don't go."],[2462,2563,"It's too dangerous."],[2660,2765,"I'm about to win."],[3190,3336,"I'm about to win."],[3812,3908,"Boss,"],[3908,4030,"I found Eliza Stone."],[4030,4210,"She's the one who went to go see Zoe."],[4504,4587,"So, it really was you."]],"48":[[129,254,"Mr. Walker, everything's right."],[333,429,"I'm heading over now."],[679,763,"Mom,"],[775,896,"Dad,"],[921,1047,"I can finally..."],[1457,1579,"Let me go!"],[2706,2800,"Let me go."],[2846,2977,"Let me go!"],[3194,3299,"It took me"],[3315,3471,"so long to find you."],[3482,3570,"What do you want?"],[3591,3707,"I really should've known"],[3707,3862,"you are their daughter."],[3883,3950,"Such a pity."],[4095,4179,"Why couldn't you have just died"],[4179,4270,"in the shootout, huh?"]],"49":[[16,171,"So, he knows everything."],[187,327,"You only have yourself to blame"],[357,454,"for giving me a chance to"],[454,517,"make you pay."],[675,729,"Please."],[763,921,"But nobody like you..."],[984,1051,"Take me down?"],[1197,1347,"Give me the USB or die."],[1372,1526,"I know nothing about a USB."],[1659,1847,"Stubborn, just like your cop parents."],[2152,2210,"I know."],[2248,2339,"But"],[2339,2465,"my decision's been made."],[2640,2731,"You would do the same thing"],[2731,2802,"if it were you."],[3474,3557,"Boss."],[3603,3724,"It's been ringing non-stop."],[3724,3883,"If it's spam, I don't care."],[4229,4379,"Oh, come on, pick up!"],[4466,4600,"Eliza could be in danger!"],[4804,4909,"Okay, you look constipated."],[4909,4979,"Just say it."],[5017,5067,"Well,"],[5067,5250,"you know that old man Eliza was with?"],[5351,5409,"I..."],[5447,5497,"What?"],[5872,5980,"Your parents are so nosy,"],[5980,6164,"always investigating our company."],[6206,6272,"But to be fair,"],[6272,6385,"it wasn't the old man's fault."],[6406,6539,"If he wasn't so interested in"],[6539,6627,"Ryder's mother's death,"],[6627,6752,"your parents never would've died."],[6785,6918,"So if you want to blame someone,"],[6948,7113,"blame my father or blame Ryder."],[7123,7176,"Shut up!"],[7219,7340,"You brought this upon yourself."],[7357,7407,"You monster!"],[7407,7507,"Oh, please!"],[7507,7655,"I did your parents a favor!"],[7671,7766,"Bang! Bang!"],[7791,7849,"Quick!"],[7857,7932,"Clean!"],[7991,8062,"Dad!"],[8112,8183,"Dad?"],[8229,8299,"Mom!"],[8404,8475,"You're the devil!"],[8516,8666,"God will punish you for this!"]],"50":[[141,250,"That's right, Eliza."],[250,329,"I am the devil."],[358,454,"And if you wanna survive,"],[454,639,"you will give me the USB."],[784,928,"In your fucking dreams!"],[928,980,"Mm-hmm."],[1947,2047,"Oh,"],[2047,2173,"you don't wanna talk?"],[2173,2248,"That's fine."],[2585,2651,"Then die."],[2932,2994,"Stop!"],[3174,3265,"Here to play the hero?"],[3333,3393,"Eliza!"],[3403,3457,"Ryder, stop!"],[3457,3596,"This has nothing to do with you!"],[3599,3676,"Get out of here!"],[3694,3743,"Eliza!"],[4542,4611,"Stop, Ryder!"],[4829,5032,"One more step, and she dies."],[5140,5205,"Fine."],[5226,5292,"Hold him down."]],"51":[[325,491,"You have no idea"],[491,580,"the joy it brings me"],[625,821,"to know that you and your filthy mother"],[821,1046,"will have died in my hands."],[1046,1184,"It was really you?"],[1272,1354,"You bastard!"],[1354,1418,"Why?"],[1418,1505,"Shut up!"],[1559,1810,"I hate that word bastard."],[1826,2014,"Why should you be there for just existing"],[2031,2137,"when I have to work twice as hard"],[2137,2239,"to be in second place?"],[2594,2685,"This is your room."],[2957,3123,"Are we sure that's the eldest son?"],[3194,3340,"Looks so shabby."],[3350,3432,"I heard his mom"],[3432,3566,"was a prostitute."],[3653,3874,"She seduced the master to have his child."],[4037,4141,"What are you talking about?"],[4141,4325,"Don't talk about my brother like that."],[4546,4650,"Such a sweet boy."],[4700,4792,"Just like your mother."],[5021,5121,"What did you think then?"],[5176,5292,"Sticking up for me would change"],[5292,5397,"what they think of me?"],[5397,5497,"Then take it out on me."],[5497,5618,"You killed my mother!"],[5634,5798,"Oh no, your mother died of a heart attack."],[5876,5985,"I just didn't give her the meds."],[6056,6076,"You-"],[6106,6348,"One more step and I'll kill her."]],"52":[[0,95,"And I'll kill her."],[179,238,"Okay."],[300,431,"Fine, you want the USB, right?"],[458,517,"That's what you want?"],[542,671,"I'll give it to you, just don't hurt her."],[1034,1132,"No, no! Don't!"],[1167,1239,"No, don't!"],[2630,2705,"You got what you wanted."],[2705,2798,"Now let her go."],[2857,2986,"Not so fast."],[2986,3086,"Lay a finger on her"],[3086,3294,"and I swear to God I'll fucking kill you!"],[3716,3802,"Kneel."],[3834,3955,"And sign the agreement"],[3955,4091,"to forfeit your inheritance,"],[4091,4270,"and maybe... Maybe!"],[4312,4408,"I'll let her go."],[4408,4496,"I'll do it."],[4593,4679,"Just don't hurt her."]],"53":[[30,91,"I'll do it."],[183,262,"Just don't hurt her."],[312,444,"Don't sign it!"],[729,850,"Don't sign it!"],[1787,1848,"Hurry up!"],[2461,2503,"Done."],[3219,3257,"Gun!"],[3699,3767,"This is for me."],[3845,3952,"This is for my mom."],[4020,4108,"And this is for Eliza."],[4575,4726,"Now you're gonna pay for it with your life."]],"54":[[672,751,"Don't move!"],[800,892,"Mr. Hawke,"],[892,967,"you're under arrest"],[967,1121,"with multiple accounts of murder,"],[1134,1272,"unlawful imprisonment,"],[1272,1434,"and corporate crimes."],[1443,1584,"You have the right to remain silent."],[1614,1693,"No, no, no, no, no."],[1693,1785,"You have the wrong guy."],[1785,1852,"No, it was him."],[1855,1906,"Nope."],[1972,2174,"Eliza had Mr. Walker hand the USB"],[2174,2304,"to the police days ago."],[2318,2382,"What?"],[2952,3182,"Yeah, that day meeting with Eliza,"],[3265,3397,"it was just to distract you."],[3678,3782,"You set me up?"],[3795,3921,"You're goddamn right, I did."],[4108,4281,"You already knew everything, didn't you?"],[4376,4485,"Yep."],[4567,4692,"I'm going to her."],[4892,5055,"This wasn't as safe, but"],[5075,5155,"it's empty."],[5167,5230,"No."],[5280,5401,"It's too dangerous."],[5497,5593,"I have a plan."],[5593,5789,"But I need you to help me leave Everon"],[5789,5922,"and distract Vincent."],[6172,6235,"You're a fool."],[6255,6377,"Good luck in prison, asshole."],[6377,6468,"You set me up!"],[6510,6620,"I'll make you pay, Ryder!"],[6765,6844,"Eliza!"],[6927,6998,"Eliza, are you okay?"]],"55":[[91,279,"Eliza, are you okay?"],[300,368,"Yeah."],[519,608,"Eliza?"],[682,762,"Eliza!"],[840,928,"Get help!"],[955,1067,"Eliza!"],[1497,1609,"Eliza!"],[1697,1913,"Don't ever leave me again."],[1952,2004,"Okay?"],[2014,2114,"After full investigation,"],[2114,2338,"Police confirms that the Stone couple"],[2338,2619,"was not killed in a gang crossfire."],[2623,2788,"Vincent Hawke has confessed"],[2788,2909,"and has been sentenced."],[2909,3019,"Dad,"],[3090,3132,"Mom,"],[3132,3319,"Vincent finally got what he deserved."],[3365,3432,"Eliza."],[3941,4040,"Let me be your protector."],[4358,4433,"Will you marry me?"],[4471,4487,"I..."]],"56":[[196,313,"What are you doing here, old man?"],[342,496,"I told you I'm not gonna be heir so..."],[496,538,"Get out!"],[604,688,"Ryder, please."],[750,838,"Miss Stone, how are you feeling?"],[900,1021,"Mr. Hawke, if I may,"],[1059,1234,"Ryder shouldn't give up his inheritance"],[1234,1322,"and I-"],[1322,1501,"I'm staying with her, no matter what."],[1501,1584,"Do you understand me?"],[1584,1680,"Ryder."],[1743,1927,"I neglected you for most of your life."],[1939,2031,"I failed you,"],[2031,2122,"and I failed your mother."],[2189,2243,"Miss Stone,"],[2243,2344,"thank you for showing me"],[2344,2450,"Vincent's true colors."],[2477,2527,"I'm sorry."],[2565,2736,"I know an apology is not enough."],[2765,2827,"That's why I'm"],[2827,2970,"handing Everon over to you."],[3090,3161,"Ryder,"],[3169,3232,"listen to me."],[3386,3554,"You better take good care of Miss Stone"],[3653,3737,"and your child."],[3739,3804,"I will-"],[4225,4287,"Child?"],[4517,4625,"Congratulations, son."],[4729,4792,"I'm going to be a dad?"],[5463,5518,"Eliza."],[5568,5655,"Marry me."],[5697,5743,"I will."]]}